localString.value: Pirate of the Ocean Loot Box

This is the signet of the Pirates of the Ocean Star, symbolizing the brotherly bond sared between this band of Pirates. The Pirates of the Ocean Star is a group of Neutral, funloving pirates who just seek to enjoy the simple pleasures of life, lute, and, of course, a good Ale.
We are the pirates of the Ocean Star We have an enormous bar With four kegs of fine beer We are strong and have no fear Sun on our backs, wind in our sails We hang onto the Ocean Stars' rails Yerning for adventure and lots of loot All who oppose we will give the boot Strength in numbers we stand togheter Loyal to one another forever Should a Blacksky arise A Star will be its demise
Please only take what you need, and please donate items that you might think would be useful to new Pirates.
